# GoRouter

LexMastery uses GoRouter exclusively.

---

# Route Ownership

Each feature registers its own routes.

Example

authentication/routes/

dashboard/routes/

quiz/routes/

---

# App Router

Only AppRouter combines routes.

Never define routes in main.dart.

---

# Guards

Implement:

Authentication

Onboarding

Subscription (future)

Maintenance Mode

---

# Route Constants

All route names belong in:

core/navigation/app_routes.dart

Never hardcode route strings.

---

# Deep Links

Support:

Courses

Lessons

AI Chats

Quizzes

Flashcards

Mock Exams

Profile

---

# Nested Navigation

Use ShellRoute for:

Bottom Navigation

Navigation Rail

Tablet Navigation

---

# Analytics

Every navigation emits analytics.

---

# Cursor Instructions

Generate feature routes.

Register with AppRouter.

Never use Navigator.push().